FBIS4-12618 "drnes069_o_94001" FBIS-NES-94-069 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 SYRIA Yemeni Presidential Council Delegation Visits Yemeni Presidential Council Delegation Visits Requests Help To End Crisis NC0804195294 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1910 GMT 8 Apr 94 NC0804195294 Cairo MENA Arabic BFN [Text] Damascus, 8 Apr (MENA)--Yemeni Presidential Council Member Salim Salih Muhammad has said that he requested Syrian participation in the military committee or in any political activity to resolve Yemen's political crisis. The Yemeni official was speaking to a MENA correspondent in Damascus after his meeting with Syrian Vice President 'Abd-al-Halim Khaddam this evening. He said Syrian officials are now studying the Yemeni request. Muhammad described his meeting with the Syrian vice president, which was attended by Syrian Foreign Minister Faruq al-Shar', as positive. The Yemeni official is visiting Syria as part of an Arab tour.
